Why do you want, need, or deserve this scholarship?
My research interests are exactly in the fields of deep learning and computer vision. My background is on physics (I have a PhD degree in theoretical physics), and I would like to use my physics technical background to benefit the neural networks research. I would also like to bring my contribution to creating the AI for a better and safer future that will benefit all of the people. I believe that this scholarship will help me learn to develop and deploy new solutions to some of these cutting-edge technologies.

Please describe in greater detail how you anticipate this scholarship would impact your life and work. 
My intention is to make a career change from my current academia position to the tech-industry and to work on deep learning and computer vision applications, and I believe that this scholarship will play an important role in helping me to achieve that.
